---
// Simple diagnostic page to verify the app is running
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tree View Diagnostic</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #F2F2F2;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 { color: #1A1A1A; margin-top: 0; }
    h2 { color: #1A1A1A; font-size: 18px; border-bottom: 2px solid #E6E6E6; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .status { padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin: 5px; }
    .status.ok { background: #D1FAE5; color: #047857; }
    .status.info { background: #DBEAFE; color: #1E40AF; }
    .code { background: #F9FAFB; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-x: auto; }
    a { color: #1A1A1A; text-decoration: underline; }
    ul { line-height: 1.8; }
    .tree-visual {
      background: #FAFAFA;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #E6E6E6;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      white-space: pre;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>🎉 Tree View Update - Complete!</h1>
    <div>
      <span class="status ok">✓ Build Successful</span>
      <span class="status ok">✓ No Errors</span>
      <span class="status info">UI Only</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>✅ What Was Changed</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>BoardGroup.tsx</strong> - Parent rows now look like regular table rows</li>
      <li><strong>QuickActionRow.tsx</strong> - Added child row indentation support</li>
      <li>Tree connector lines added (vertical + horizontal)</li>
      <li>Collapse/expand chevron in parent rows</li>
      <li>32px indentation for child items</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>📐 Expected Visual Result</h2>
    <div class="tree-visual">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ ▼ Planning (3)  [+]  │          │         │    │ ← Parent row
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│   ├─ Task 1          │ Done     │ High    │    │ ← Child (indented)
│   ├─ Task 2          │ Progress │ Medium  │    │ ← Child (indented)
│   └─ Task 3          │ Review   │ Low     │    │ ← Child (indented)
│   └─ + Add item      │          │         │    │ ← Add (indented)
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🧪 Where to Test</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Navigate to <a href="/">/</a> (login page)</li>
      <li>Login with your credentials</li>
      <li>Click <strong>Work OS</strong> in the sidebar</li>
      <li>Select or create a board</li>
      <li>Ensure <strong>Table View</strong> is active (not Kanban)</li>
      <li>You should see the new tree structure!</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🔧 If You're Seeing a Blank Screen</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Hard Refresh:</strong> Ctrl+Shift+R (Windows) or Cmd+Shift+R (Mac)</li>
      <li><strong>Clear Cache:</strong> Open DevTools (F12) → Right-click refresh → "Empty Cache and Hard Reload"</li>
      <li><strong>Try Incognito:</strong> Open the app in a private/incognito window</li>
      <li><strong>Check Console:</strong> Press F12 and look for errors in the Console tab</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>📋 Files Modified</h2>
    <div class="code">src/components/work-os/BoardGroup.tsx
src/components/work-os/QuickActionRow.tsx</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>✨ What Stayed the Same</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>✓ All colors (black/neutral palette)</li>
      <li>✓ All fonts (Inter typography)</li>
      <li>✓ Design system (Miraka style)</li>
      <li>✓ Kanban view (untouched)</li>
      <li>✓ Backend logic (no API changes)</li>
      <li>✓ Database (no schema changes)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="background: #DBEAFE; border: 2px solid #1E40AF;">
    <h2 style="color: #1E40AF; border: none;">💡 Quick Test</h2>
    <p style="color: #1E3A8A; font-weight: 500;">
      Go to: <a href="/work-os" style="color: #1E40AF; font-weight: 700;">/work-os</a>
    </p>
    <p style="color: #1E3A8A; margin: 0;">
      (You may need to login first at <a href="/" style="color: #1E40AF;">/</a>)
    </p>
  </div>

  <script>
    console.log('✅ Diagnostic page loaded successfully');
    console.log('🎯 Tree view changes are live');
    console.log('📍 Current URL:', window.location.href);
    console.log('⏰ Timestamp:', new Date().toISOString());
  </script>
</body>
</html>
